query:
SELECT qp.questionId, qp.firstAttemptStatus, qp.lastAttemptCorrect, q.questionText
FROM question_progress qp
JOIN questions q ON qp.questionId = q.id
WHERE qp.userId = (SELECT id FROM users WHERE email = 'testyou@me.com')
  AND q.questionText LIKE '%Anhang%gef채hrlich%'
LIMIT 1;
